<p class="ql-align-justify">盼星星盼月亮</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">介次ta终于来东门啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">包下了四层楼</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大写的豪气！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">再也不用跨大半个成都去西门排长队！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200903/51b9ea8caf1144ca81cf79d8d48e6243.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>东门首店川西坝子万科天荟黑金3.0直营店</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">9.6即将开业</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">你准备好了吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200903/248f742df9df44a7a3434755e1633725.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">传承地道四川火锅文化</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">是童年记忆中的味道</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">……</p>
